<section>
<b>
Cohousing in Aotearoa New Zealand
</b>
</section>
Other housing developments founded on cohousing or cooperative principles include:
<li> Riverside community (Moutere, 1941) </li>
<li> Creekside community (Christchurch, 1974) </li>
<li> Peterborough Housing Cooperative (Christchurch, 1982) </li>
<li> Earthsong (Auckland, 2008) </li>
<li> High Street Cohousing (Dunedin, 2022) </li>
<li> Takaka Cohousing (Golden Bay, 2023) </li>
</p>

