<h4> Operation </h4>
<p>
Cohaus was designed to be run by residents for residents and in practice it actually is!
The Body Corporate utilises residents in un-paid and paid positions to do the operational and maintenance work normally outsourced to a Property Manager
Utilities management system is monitored and adapted by the residents
</p>

<p>
<section>
<b>Studio Nord </b>
</section>
Thom Gill, Helle Westergaard
</p>


<p>
<section>
<b>Site Area</b>
</section>
2407 m2
</p>

<p>
<section>
<b>
Total building area
</b>
</section>
3352 m2 of which
<ul>
<li>
1706 m2 in 20 units
1646 m2 common areas
Plus 260 m2 private external decks and patios
</li>
</ul>
</p>



